      "message": "This is probably little cleaner if you use a separate compose file (and maybe `extends`). You probably also want to use different ports?\n\n`compose-summit26.yml`\n``` \nservices:\n  summit-2026:\n    extends:\n      file: docker-compose.yml\n      service: server\n    volumes:\n      - \"./summit/2026:/site\"\n      - \"./_site/summit26:/site/_site\" # this lets you avoid setting `-d /output`\n```",
